sb-layout-dashboard
    sb-dashboard-head(title='System', i18n-title="@@system", [hideBreadcrumbs]='true')
    sb-common-cards([notificationEvents]="notificationSubject.asObservable()", (serviceRetry)="onServiceRetry($event)")
    sb-card
        .card-body
            span(i18n="@@systemInfo") This board allows you to configure the system parameters.

    sb-card
        .card-header
            fa-icon.mr-1([icon]='["fas", "laptop"]')
            | Versions
        .card-body
            | Front-End version : {{frontEndVersion}}
            | <br/>
            div.spinner-border(*ngIf='backEndVersion === undefined  && backEndVersionOnError === false', role='status')
                span(i18n='@@loading').sr-only Loading...
            div(*ngIf='backEndVersion !== undefined || backEndVersionOnError === true')
                | Back-End version
                | {{' '}}:{{' '}}
                span(*ngIf='backEndVersion !== undefined') {{backEndVersion}}
                span(*ngIf='backEndVersionOnError === true',i18n='@@informationNotAvailable') Information not available
